IMAPStore govanify-remote
Host govanify.com
Port  993
User gauvain@govanify.com
PassCmd "pass navi/gauvain@govanify.com | head -n 1"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt 

MaildirStore govanify-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/govanify/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/govanify/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel govanify
Expunge Both
Master :govanify-remote:
Slave :govanify-local:
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
Patterns *
# End profile

